properties.stageStory: "That place was so strange that the water was... purple?"
"There was something familiar in that palace. Is here where the stars are made?"
"No time to explain! Just run and get all the stars!"
"Starcat fell in a hole and found himself in a hot, hot underground palace..."
"A flood sank the stars under the water! What a mess, Starcat!"
"Once upon a time, a yellow cat named Starcat was collecting all the stars as usual..."
